high_descs: Turn around and walk to the cabinet with the spray bottles on top.
Pick up the white spray bottle, on the right front.
Turn right for three steps, turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and face the toilet.
Put the spray bottle, facing the wall, on top of the toilet tank, in line with the flush handle.
Turn right for two steps, turn left for two steps, turn right and back to the cabinet with the spray bottles on top.
Pick up the spray bottle in the back.
Turn right for three steps, turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and face the toilet.
Put the spray bottle, facing the wall, right in front of the green soap bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two white spray bottles on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: look down and turn right and walk straight towards the table
pick up the spray bottle on the right side of the table
turn right and walk towards the tub and then turn right again and walk straight towards the wall and turn right again and look up at the toilet
put the spray bottle on the top of the toilet
walk straight then turn right and walk straight then turn left towards the door then turn right towards the table and walk straight
pick up the spray bottle in the back of the table
turn right then walk straight towards the tub then turn right and walk straight towards the wall then turn right again towards the toilet
put the spray bottle down next to the other spray bottle on the top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: clean up spray bottles and put them on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right and face the cabinets in front of you.
Take the spray bottle from the cabinet in front of you.
Turn around and face the toilet on your right.
Place the spray bottle on top of the toilet.
Turn right and face the cabinet in front of you.
Take the spray bottle from the cabinet in front of you.
Turn around and face the toilet to your right.
Place the spray bottle on top of the toilet in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place spray bottles on top of the toilet.
